NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ScriptX - Plugin to use when building ScriptX::*
    distribution

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ScriptX
    (from Perl distribution Dist-Zilla-Plugin-ScriptX), released on
    2019-12-25.

SYNOPSIS
    In dist.ini:

     [ScriptX]

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin is to be used when building "ScriptX::*" distribution. It
    currently does the following:

    *   Fill the Abstract from meta's summary

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Dist-Zilla-Plugin-ScriptX>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Dist-Zilla-Plugin-ScriptX>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Scr
    iptX>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

